quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  103,1,By the time
  103,2,man is in utter loss
  103,3,"except those who believe and do righteous deeds, and exhort one another to the truth and exhort one another to patience"
  104,1,Woe to every backbiter and slanderer
  104,2,who amasses wealth and counts it over and again
  104,3,thinking that his wealth will make him live forever
  104,4,No indeed! He will surely be cast into the Crushing Fire
  104,5,and how do you know what the Crushing Fire is
  104,6,It is the kindled Fire of Allah
  104,7,which reaches the hearts
  104,8,It will be closed down upon them
  104,9,locked with towering columns
  105,1,Have you not seen how your Lord dealt with the people of the Elephant
  105,2,Did He not turn their scheme into a total loss
  105,3,He sent against them swarms of birds
  105,4,pelting them with stones of baked clay
  105,5,leaving them like chewed up and trampled chaff